These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cucumber, carrot, potato, lemon, grapefruit
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, family, satire, western, zombie
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, board-games, singing, camping, video-games
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, iris, azalea, amaryllis
 1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
 2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
 5. the person who growstulip is the person watching crime movies##1
 6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1
10. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person eating grapefruit is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person watching zombie movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Food      | cucumber        | carrot | grapefruit     | potato   | lemon |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | family      | western | zombie   | crime    |
| Hobby   | camping  | board-games     | sudoku | singing | video-games  |
| Flower           | marigold | iris      | amaryllis     | azalea   | tulip     |

