.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: gardening, hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, kale, avocado, peach, pomegranate
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, bellflower, daffodil, orchid
5 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, snooker, scrabble, bridge
 1. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who growsazalea and the person eating pomegranate##2
 6. the person playing scrabble is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
10. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's hobby is reading##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | gardening | writing    | hiking  | reading    |
| Food   | pomegranate    | kale       | avocado      | cranberry | peach        |
| Flower   | orchid   | tulip     | azalea    | daffodil  | bellflower     |
| Game     | snooker    | mah-jongg | bridge | scrabble | backgammon |

