.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There 5 different types of food: cucumber, garlic, grapefruit, cauliflower, orange
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, designer, project-manager, librarian, architect
House: palace, futuristic, townhouse, tower, art-deco
 1. the person eating orange is the designer##1
 2. the tower house is in the middle##1
 3. the librarian is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person eating orange is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person eating garlic is on the left of the fisherman##1
 7. the architect is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the project-manager is on the far left##1
10. the palace house is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the art-deco house##1
12. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the architect##1
13. the art-deco house is between the person watching superhero movies and the person eating grapefruit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Food         | cucumber | orange     | grapefruit   | garlic   | cauliflower |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
| Job   | project-manager      | designer      | librarian       | architect       | fisherman       |
| House         | futuristic | art-deco  | tower    | palace    | townhouse        |

