.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
City: marseilles, miami, colone, nizza, london
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, subway, ship, helicopter
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, action, martial-arts, documentary, family
 1. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person watching family movies is between the fan of reggae and the person traveling to nizza##2
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
12. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| City          | london  | colone     | nizza   | miami     | marseilles |
| Transport         | helicopter | skateboard    | subway  | ship | motorbike   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | documentary | family | romance   |

