 1. the italian is on the right of the dancer##1
 2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the pakistani##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the dutch##1
 4. the person who likes black is between the italian and the davidoff-smoker##2
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the nigerian##1
 6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes pink is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the nigerian##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
