 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the fan of pop##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growstulip and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of disco##1
