The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, boat, airplane, scooter
There are 5 different nationalities: french, indian, italian, polish, thai
 1. the polish is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the indian##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is the italian##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the italian##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the italian is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the french##1
11. the person driving the boat is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person drinking coffee##2
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
| Beverage         | coffee      | lemonade | soy-milk | cola | water |
| Birthday   | october | january  | february        | november   | july |
| Transport   | scooter      | boat       | jet-ski     | airplane    | van   |
| Nationality   | italian     | indian    | polish      | thai    | french  |

