.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, spinach, tomato, banana, pomegranate
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, designer, doctor, security-guard
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, fuchsia, amber, lavender, brown
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the person who likes brown is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 2. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 3. the person eating spinach is the doctor##1
 4. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 6. the doctor is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the designer is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 9. the dancer is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person who likes amber and the designer##2
12. the person eating banana is on the right of the security-guard##1
13. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Food    | tomato       | banana    | pomegranate | spinach  | asparagus        |
| Job       | security-guard | dancer | designer  | doctor | fisherman    |
| Color       | amber        | lavender   | fuchsia  | brown   | light-blue |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

