.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, alhambra, havana, fonseca, aristoff
There 5 different types of food: apricot, pomegranate, strawberry, pepper, zucchini
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, turquise, lavender, emerald, fuchsia
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 2. the person eating pepper is between the person who likes lavender and the person eating strawberry##2
 3. the fonseca-smoker is the person eating pepper##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
 6. the fonseca-smoker is between the person eating zucchini and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
10. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person eating strawberry is the person who likes turquise##1
12. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
13. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar      | baccarat      | alhambra         | fonseca      | havana | aristoff     |
| Food           | pomegranate | strawberry | pepper | zucchini    | apricot  |
| Color   | emerald  | turquise    | blood-red | lavender    | fuchsia |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

