.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
House: tower, townhouse, cottage, palace, gothic-revival
5 different games are played: canasta, whist, poker, snooker, bridge
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, epic, sports, scientific, horror
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the person playing canasta and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
 7. the cottage house is between the person watching zombie movies and the gothic-revival house##2
 8. the townhouse house is between the palace house and the tower house##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the tower house##1
10. the tower house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| House         | gothic-revival  | cottage | palace   | townhouse      | tower |
| Game   | canasta   | snooker    | whist | bridge | poker      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Movie-Genre     | sports | horror        | zombie  | epic        | scientific    |

