.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, december, april, october, may
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, lilac, mauve, red, turquise
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, fonseca, vegafina, havana, cain
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 2. the person who likes turquise is between the havana-smoker and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the cain-smoker and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who likes mauve is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the fan of blues##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is the fan of blues##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the person who likes lilac is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Birthday         | april    | may  | december  | june      | october |
| Color   | lilac    | turquise   | red | mauve | blue   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Cigar   | havana  | fonseca | cain    | vegafina     | chaman      |

 